m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This weapon is a +3 furious double axe. If the wielder has the barbarian rage class ability, it allows them to use it for 4 additional {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g} per day.

__root.Comment: This +3 furious double axe grants the wearer 4 additional round of Rage per day.

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This weapon is a +5/+5 double axe. Whenever its first blade lands a hit, it marks the target for an execution. Whenever the second blade hits a marked target, it removes the mark and deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d10{/g} + wielder's {g|Encyclopedia:Strength}Strength{/g} modifier {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g}.

__root.Comment: Double axe +5/+5, когда первая часть попадает - кладет на цель бафф, когда попадает вторая часть - бафф снимается, наносится 1d10+Strength

m_DescriptionText.LocalisedValue: This +1 cold iron orc double axe deals additional 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Energy_Damage}cold damage{/g} with one end and 1 sonic {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} with the other.
Whenever the wielder of this +3 furyborn greatsword is under a rage effect, she doesn't suffer from its usual -2 {g|Encyclopedia:Penalty}penalty{/g} to {g|Encyclopedia:Armor_Class}AC{/g}.

Whenever this +3 double axe lands a hit with its head, if the next {g|Encyclopedia:Attack}attack{/g} with the tail also lands a hit, it deals additional {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}1d12{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Damage_Type}slashing damage{/g}.

Whenever the wielder of this +4 vicious double axe lands a killing blow on an enemy, all enemies in a 15-foot area suffer {g|Encyclopedia:Dice}4d6{/g} sonic {g|Encyclopedia:Damage}damage{/g} and become frightened for 1 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}round{/g}. Successful {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Will saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 27) halves the damage and negates fear.

Successful {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Will saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 27) halves the damage and negates fear.

Whenever the wielder of this +5 nullifying double axe lands a {g|Encyclopedia:Critical}critical hit{/g}, the enemy must must pass a {g|Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw}Will saving throw{/g} ({g|Encyclopedia:DC}DC{/g} 30) or become unable to cast {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spells{/g} for 2 {g|Encyclopedia:Combat_Round}rounds{/g}.
